text.tspan: CLOSEST DRAFT PINT ON RAPID RAIL
The map shows the bar closest by pedestrian distance to the
rapid transit stop and price of the cheapest 16oz pint on draft.
* Bar must have draft on tap and be within a 20 minute walk of transit station.
